Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill will require you to have an existing account with C+R research. Please contact C+R Research at alexa@crresearch.com, if you don't have an account and would like to join. 

You will need to use the C+R research account in Account Linking. You won't be able to use this skill without Account Linking.

This skill will allow you to participate in ethnographic in-home research projects.
